Phonak sees 97 / 98 sales , profit up c . 20pct . Swiss hearing aid company Phonak Holding AG said it expected sales and profit to rise by around 20 percent in the 1997 / 98 business year ending on March 31 . " In the current year we again expect strong , primarily internal , sales growth of around 20 percent so that sales could top the 200 million Swiss franc level for the first time , " it said . " Group profit should rise roughly in line with sales . " The company said 1996 / 97 profit will be steady around 17 . 5 million francs on sales of 171 million , up from 132 million . - - Zurich newsroom + 41 1 631 7340 
